Lyrics-Fetcher-LyricWiki version 0.01
====================================

Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricWiki, as the name suggests, fetches lyrics
from www.LyricWiki.org using the SOAP Web Service.

It is intended to be used as a fetcher by Lyrics::Fetcher, but
can be used on its own if you desire.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  SOAP::Lite
  
Calling Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricWiki via Lyrics::Fetcher->fetch() is
recommended, but you can call Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricWiki->fetch() directly
if you want to do so.


